 ing or slowing.\n\n• Frequency: Quarterly\, with revisions.\n\n• Not
 es: GDP can be backward-looking\, so markets often react more strongly w
 hen the result changes the outlook for central-bank policy or recession 
 risk.\n\n• Acronyms: GDP = Gross Domestic Product.\n\nOfficial source:
  https://www.abs.gov.au/release-calendar/future-releases/202606/all
