 or Australia\, Labour Force data is important for RBA expectations.\n\n
 • Acronyms: NFP = Non-Farm Payrolls\; ABS = Australian Bureau of Stati
 stics\; BLS = Bureau of Labor Statistics.\n\nOfficial source: https://ww
 w.abs.gov.au/release-calendar/future-releases/202611
